<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.10">
<l>kaṇṇā yēḻulakuk kuyirāyaveṅ kārvaṇṇaṉai</l>
<l>viṇṇōrt tāmparavum poḻilvēṅkaṭa vētiyaṉai</l>
<l>tiṇṇār māṭaṅkaḷcūḻ tirumaṅkaiyark kōṉkaliyaṉ</l>
<l>paṇṇārp pāṭalpattum payilvārkkillai pāvaṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who recite these ten melodious songs of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l>King of those of Maṅkai with stout mansions, on our cloud-colored one</l>
<l>Who became the body and the soul of the seven worlds,</l>
<l>The Vedic sage of gardened Vēṅkaṭa whom the celestials praise,</l>
<l rend="indent">sins do not exist.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
